channel.title: Some Models I made
channel.description:
Well, I always get compliments on my server because we have Fight gear, Dress up gear, poor looking gear, rich gear, and much more items.
But someone walked up to me the other day and told me that there needs to be more dress up gear, considering we only had the tuxedo I made these, problem is, I don't know how to animate them o.o so when I equip them in game, I go invisible.
